---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Aveliq covers AI, finance and fintech. Signal over noise.">
  <section class="about">

    <div class="about-hero">
      <div class="about-eyebrow">About</div>
      <h1 class="about-h1">Signal<br>over noise.</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="about-body">

      <div class="about-block">
        <div class="about-block-label">Mission</div>
        <div class="about-block-content">
          <p>Aveliq covers artificial intelligence, technology, markets, and the ideas shaping the future. Our mission is to filter noise, identify important signals, and deliver clear analysis for curious readers.</p>
          <p>We write for investors, operators, and technologists who need context, not headlines.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-block">
        <div class="about-block-label">Editorial Standards</div>
        <div class="about-block-content">
          <p>We prioritize accuracy, transparency, and context. Every story is reviewed for clarity and factual consistency. We separate reporting from opinion and update articles when new information becomes available.</p>
          <p>We do not accept payment for editorial coverage. Sponsored content is always clearly labelled.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-block">
        <div class="about-block-label">Author</div>
        <div class="about-block-content">
          <div class="author-card">
            <div class="author-av">AR</div>
            <div>
              <div class="author-name">Alex Reeve</div>
              <div class="author-role">Editor · Aveliq</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>Alex Reeve is an independent writer and editor focused on emerging technologies, AI, and digital finance. His work explores how technology influences business, markets, and everyday life.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.about-hero {
  background: var(--bg2);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--b);
  padding: 60px 40px 48px;
}

.about-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: .14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--amber);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.about-h1 {
  font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px);
  line-height: .95;
  letter-spacing: .02em;
  color: var(--paper);
}

.about-body {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 40px 80px;
}

.about-block {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
  gap: 40px;
  padding: 48px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--b);
}

.about-block-label {
  font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: .12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--amber);
  padding-top: 4px;
}

.about-block-content p {
  font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  color: rgba(245,240,232,.7);
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.about-block-content p:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.author-card {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  padding: 20px;
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--b);
}

.author-av {
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  background: var(--amber);
  color: var(--ink);
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 700;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.author-name {
  font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--paper);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.author-role {
  font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  color: rgba(245,240,232,.35);
  letter-spacing: .06em;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .about-hero { padding: 40px 20px 32px; }
  .about-body { padding: 0 20px 60px; }
  .about-block { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
}
</style>